thread.title: DocuSign Files for IPO

author: Maria Armental
title: DocuSign Files for IPO
text:
Electronic-signature technology company DocuSign Inc. has filed preliminary documents for an initial public offering.
If its IPO takes place, DocuSign would join other expected newcomers from the club of startups valued at more than $1 billion, such as Spotify. Dropbox Inc. and Zscaler Inc., which are also so-called unicorns, debuted this month.
